{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Make all marketplace tile headers consistent h-20 height (#1576)\n\nNon-CNCF tiles (themes, dashboards, card presets) were h-36 while\nCNCF tiles with logos were h-20, causing uneven grid alignment.\nNow all tiles use h-20 headers for a consistent layout.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
